<h3 id="how-to-contact-the-data-protection-officer">How to contact the Data Protection Officer</h3>

<p>DFID have appointed a Data Protection Officer (DPO) who is responsible for how the organisation handles personal information.</p>

<p>If you have any concerns about how DFID handle your personal information, please contact our Data Protection Officer.</p>

